### ==== NOTIFICATIONS API ====
# Docs: http://localhost:5000/scalar/v1
# Base routes:
#   /api/v1/notifications                         — user-facing (Authenticated)
#   /api/v1/admin/notification-templates          — template admin (SystemAdmin/TenantAdmin)
#
# Channel values: InApp, Email, Sms, Push

# ── User Notifications ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List my notifications (paged)
# userId resolved from JWT sub claim — no userId param needed
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications?tenantId={{tenantId}}&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List unread notifications only
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications?tenantId={{tenantId}}&isRead=false&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List notifications filtered by channel
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications?tenantId={{tenantId}}&channel=InApp&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get unread notification count (for badge display)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications/unread-count?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Mark a single notification as read
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001/read?tenantId={{tenantId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Send notification (programmatic — SystemAdmin/TenantAdmin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "recipientUserId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
  "subject": "Your case has been approved",
  "body": "Case #ABC12345 has been reviewed and approved. Please check the portal for details.",
  "channel": "InApp",
  "templateId": null,
  "correlationId": "case-00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001"
}

###

### Send notification using a template
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "recipientUserId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
  "subject": "Case status update",
  "body": "Your case has been updated.",
  "channel": "Email",
  "templateId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "correlationId": null
}

# ── Notification Templates Admin ─────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### List notification templates for a tenant (SystemAdmin/TenantAdmin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/notification-templates?tenantId={{tenantId}}&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### List templates filtered by channel
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/notification-templates?tenantId={{tenantId}}&channel=Email&page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Create notification template (SystemAdmin/TenantAdmin)
# SubjectTemplate and BodyTemplate support {{variable}} placeholders
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/notification-templates
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenantId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "templateKey": "case.approved",
  "subjectTemplate": "Case {{caseNumber}} has been approved",
  "bodyTemplate": "Dear {{fullName}},\n\nYour case {{caseNumber}} submitted on {{submittedDate}} has been approved.\n\nPlease log in to the portal to view the full decision.",
  "channel": "Email"
}
